{"tid":2059294,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"布拉格爆發反政府示威抗議總統親中 現場有人舉起台灣中華民國旗","createTime":"2020-06-10T22:23:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T07:26:57.000Z","uid":357030,"like":122,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"13a017705ed6088112b058b1f2f37d76cd8bfd0a","tid":2059294,"uid":357030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T22:23:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dexWa3D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdexWa3D.jpg&h=249ebd44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在周二傍晚，有1500-3000人在老城廣場（Old Town Square）集會，對深陷貪污舞弊醜聞的總理巴比斯(Andrej Babi&scaron;)及執政聯盟表達不滿，包括應對武漢肺炎疫情及紓困振興不力、過度向北京傾斜及多項措施侵蝕民主制度。<br />\n<br />\n示威者不滿國會近日未能通過「感謝台灣」決議案及親北京的執政聯盟拒絕正式感謝台灣，現場除可聽見「謝謝台灣」口號，還可見一、兩面青天白日滿地紅旗飄揚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200611/EGUAB6H3WCYYXNQOMXIDYG37DI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200611%2FEGUAB6H3WCYYXNQOMXIDYG37DI%2F&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRCZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=3361c5b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200611%2FEGUAB6H3WCYYXNQOMXIDYG37DI%2F&h=d5f4a4c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200611/EGUAB6H3WCYYXNQOMXIDYG37DI/</a>"},{"pid":"f2ad26999e3e9348b3ae422410f4697009ee14b1","tid":2059294,"uid":158888,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T22:40:49.000Z","msg":"快啲踢走奶共總理"},{"pid":"6d6a6fa4e606ea3727d4bcbdac4a643708d4a313","tid":2059294,"uid":55089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T22:47:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i